project_descr: Tuberculosis and HIV Collaborative Program in S.Sudan

outputs.output_descr: This project is aimed at establishing mechanisms for collaboration between TB and HIV/AIDS programmes, decreasing the burden of TB in people living with HIV/AIDS (PLWHA), and decreasing the burden of HIV/AIDS in TB patients.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
